{"tid":923864,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Google 員工為抗議中國版搜尋引擎開發　開始集資罷工","createTime":"2018-12-01T15:29:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-02T14:27:36.000Z","uid":47714,"like":291,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":58,"replies":[{"pid":"edb47650a48b583ebbc03611c45b517f4aea3f12","tid":923864,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T15:29:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2018/12/01/google-employee-strike-fund-pledges-dragonfly-china-search/fun-tech/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2018%2F12%2F01%2Fgoogle-employee-strike-fund-pledges-dragonfly-china-search%2Ffun-tech%2F&d=Jg%2B7rGYuEHm6f31NpujP3zPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=dff2ff48\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2018/12/01/google-employee-strike-fund-pledges-dragonfly-china-search/fun-tech/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/google-walkout.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F11%2Fgoogle-walkout.jpg&h=a9079510&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nGoogle 祕密為重新進入中國搜尋引擎市場，而開發代號為 Dragonfly 的特別版搜尋引擎，除了引起公衆爭議，Google 內部亦有大量反對聲音。最近有員工就開始集資準備進行罷工行動。<br />\n<br />\nGoogle 員工 Liz Fong-Jones 是今次發起罷工基金募資的員工，她表示 Google 員工應該思考如果高層的決定蓋過公司安全和私隱團隊的建議時，應該如何自處。而她打算發動一次罷工，因此開始集資籌備離職基金，尤其是正在領取 H1B 簽證的同事如果失去工作，將需要經濟支援。<br />\n<br />\n目前罷工基金已經募集到超過 10 萬美元的資金，來自 19 個現任員工以及 2 個離任員工。Liz Fong-Jones 自己會就金額自費配對，因此目前基金已經達到 20 萬美元的金額。她表示未來會尋求法律顧問和工會組織人士的意見，之後再公佈更多的詳情。之前在總部針對性侵犯事件的遊行中，有超過 2 萬名員工參加，如果真的出現罷工行動，會有多少人加入，仍然有哦代觀察。"},{"pid":"bc01461b8ddf1ac9f0af5db79e2ac93593c2a18c","tid":923864,"uid":35814,"like":315,"dislike":4,"score":311,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T15:43:02.000Z","msg":"其實全世界都好多人用google<br />\n真心唔明為乜仲要去奶共"},{"pid":"c647ab84266f46959c782e7e655f33eb97b81d70","tid":923864,"uid":4783,"like":33,"dislike":2,"score":31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T15:46:37.000Z","msg":"開始要慢慢停用佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 